性感帶在男性生殖器部份包括[[龜頭|龜頭]]和[[陰莖|陰莖]]兩側、龜頭上側、[[陰囊|陰囊]]的前側、陰囊和肛門之間的[[會陰|會陰]]，以及肛門附近<ref name="ncbi">{{Cite journal|title=Self-ratings of genital anatomy, sexual sensitivity and function in men using the ‘Self-Assessment of Genital Anatomy and Sexual Function, Male’ questionnaire|url=https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1111/j.1464-410X.2008.08166.x|last=Schober|first=Justine M.|last2=Meyer-Bahlburg|first2=Heino F.L.|date=2009-04|journal=BJU International|issue=8|doi=10.1111/j.1464-410X.2008.08166.x|pmid=19245445|volume=103|pages=1096–1103|language=en|last3=Dolezal|first3=Curtis}}</ref>。

